  "texts": [
    "Moreover, we evaluated how learners perceived the generated feedback by setting up a randomised control study with a cohort of learners.",
    "This revealed overall positive effects regarding highly informative feedback and that our participants were, on average, more influenced by whether they passed the formal APA requirements.",
    "Given that the participants were students from an introductory lecture, this is an expected result as they do not have extensive experience in paper writing.",
    "Nonetheless, the highly informative feedback positively affected helpfulness and reflection.",
    "A clear limitation of our approach is that the feedback is generated solely through templates."
  ],
